item.description: Works (under construction) For more information, go to bandcamp or soundcloud at the bottom of the site, or go to about. 2018/02/09 : Participated in “Shibuya-Kei Chiptune Cover Compilation” by OMOIDE LABEL x Bytedoll Records with “TWEEDEES - Baby, Baby (tobokegao Gameboy Cover) 2017/12/27 : “Gameboy Noise Jam 002 (Circuit Bent)” for “reversible chance operation”, a compilation of “one-of-a-kind” music that sounds different from one another as a result of randomly skipping oil on each CD.
